SimpleRayCasting
================

About
-----

SimpleRayCasting is a simple ray casting 3-D maze explorer written in
FreeBASIC as a learning exercise.

Controls
--------

'w' key		-	Move forward
'a' key		-	Rotate left
's' key		-	Move backward
'd' key		-	Rotate right
'x' key		-	Exit program

